Description
===========
Sample application demonstrating how to integrate send email with attachments using Spring 3.1, SendGrid, and blueimp's jQuery-File-Upload plugin

To read the whole guide, please see the original blog:

"Email with Attachments via Spring and SendGrid"
http://krams915.blogspot.com/2012/07/email-with-attachments-via-spring-and.html


Building
========
Please visit http://krams915.blogspot.com/2012/07/email-with-attachments-via-spring-and_5148.html for full instructions


